  "notes": "Route 34 is a long north-south route (10x27 blocks) connecting Goldenrod City to the north and Ilex Forest to the south via a gate building. The Day-Care Center is the primary feature, situated on the east side of the route around the midpoint. Officer Keith is a night-only trainer — he will not battle during daytime. Three Cooltrainer F sisters (Irene, Jenn, Kate) are located in a fenced water enclave at the far south-west and can only be reached via Surf. Kate gives Soft Sand after defeat, which changes dialogue for her sisters. The Day Care Man comes outside and intercepts the player when an Egg is ready; this is driven by ENGINE_DAY_CARE_MAN_HAS_EGG via the MAPCALLBACK_OBJECTS callback. Camper Todd and Picnicker Gina both have Pokegear rematch phones."
}
